	<header class=3D"entry-header">
		<h1 class=3D"entry-title">Scotch Barrel Sizes: Firkin, Kilderkin, Hogshea=
d, Butt &amp; Tun</h1>

				<div class=3D"entry-meta">
			<span class=3D"sep">Posted on </span><a href=3D"https://scotchaddict.com=
/scotch-barrel-sizes-firkin-kilderkin-hogshead-butt-tun.html" title=3D"6:57=
