tc. I have yet to visit but I=E2=80=99d love to. When I went several years =
ago we visited a few of the Speysides since they were easier to get to from=
 Edinburgh but it was a blast.</p>
<p>I have a Bunnahabhain Darach Ur sitting in my case from a previous visit=
 to the UK and I really need to do a tasting note on it. It just looks so e=
pic that I almost feel bad opening it! =F0=9F=99=82</p>
